       TESTSUITE 'Calculate REFTRAN-REMAINING-AMT for rejected transactions'

       TESTCASE 'Calculate remaining amount when transaction has no errors and no refunds'
      *GIVEN a rejected transaction record with transaction ID RTRAN-TRANS-ID of 12345678901234567890
       MOCK PARAGRAPH 2200-READ-IN
          ADD 1 TO REF-IN-CNT.
          ADD REFTRAN-CHG-AMT TO REF-IN-AMT.
          MOVE SPACES TO WS-ERR-IND.
           MOVE 12345678901234567890 TO RTRAN-TRANS-ID.
       END-MOCK.

      *AND the charges master file contains a record with:
      *" CHG-KEY             ", " CHG-ERR-IND ", " CHG-COUNT ", " CHG-AMT ", " CHG-STATE ",
      *" 12345678901234567890", " " "         ", " 0         ", " 10000   ", " FL        ",
      MOCK PARAGRAPH 2300-CONT
          MOVE RTRAN-TRANS-ID TO CHG-KEY.
          MOVE 0 TO WS-CHG-STATUS
          MOVE 12345678901234567890 TO CHG-KEY
          MOVE " " TO CHG-ERR-IND
          MOVE 0 TO CHG-COUNT
          MOVE 10000 TO CHG-AMT
          MOVE "FL" TO CHG-STATE
          IF WS-CHG-STATUS = '00'
              GO TO 2300-FOUND
          ELSE
              IF WS-CHG-STATUS = '23'
                  MOVE 'X' TO WS-ERR-IND
                  ADD 1 TO REC-NO-CHG
                  ADD REFTRAN-CHG-AMT TO AMT-NO-CHG
                  GO TO 2300-EXIT
              ELSE
                  MOVE 'X' TO WS-ERR-IND
                  GO TO 2300-EXIT.
      END-MOCK.
      *AND no surcharge paid record exists for transaction ID 12345678901234567890
      MOCK PARAGRAPH 1000-CHECK-SURCH
          MOVE RTRAN-TRANS-ID TO SURCH-KEY.
          MOVE 23 TO WS-SURCH-STATUS.
          IF WS-SURCH-STATUS = ZERO
             IF CHG-STATE IS NOT =  'CA' OR 'NY'
               MOVE 'X' TO WS-ERR-IND
             ELSE
                NEXT SENTENCE
          ELSE
             IF WS-SURCH-STATUS = 23
                NEXT SENTENCE
             ELSE
                PERFORM 9100-CLOSE THRU 9100-EXIT
                CALL 'ABEND'.
      END-MOCK.
      *AND no retailer refund records exist for transaction ID 12345678901234567890
      MOCK PARAGRAPH 2800-RETAIL
          MOVE WS-RETREF-CNT TO RETREFS-SEQ.
          MOVE CHG-KEY TO RETREFS-ID.
          MOVE 23 TO WS-RETREF-STATUS.
          IF WS-RETREF-STATUS IS EQUAL TO ZERO
             GO TO 2800-FOUND.
          IF WS-RETREF-STATUS IS EQUAL TO 23
             GO TO 2800-NOT-FOUND.
      END-MOCK.
      *AND no latest refund record exists for transaction ID 12345678901234567890
      MOCK PARAGRAPH 2400-CHECK-REFUNDS
          MOVE '0' TO WS-ERR-IND.
          MOVE ZERO TO WS-REFUND-SOFAR WS-REMAINING.
          MOVE ZERO TO WS-REFUND-FOUND-CNT.
          MOVE 0 TO WS-RETREF-CNT.
          PERFORM 2800-RETAIL THRU 2800-EXIT.
          MOVE CHG-KEY TO LATEST-REF-KEY.
          MOVE 23 TO WS-LATEST-STATUS.
          IF WS-LATEST-STATUS IS EQUAL TO ZERO
             GO TO 200-REFUND-TODAY.
          IF WS-LATEST-STATUS IS EQUAL TO 23
             GO TO 200-NO-REFUND-TODAY.
     END-MOCK.

      *WHEN 200-READ-INPUT is performed
      MOCK PARAGRAPH 200-WRITE
          ADD 1 TO TOT-OUT-CNT.
          ADD REFTRAN-CHG-AMT TO TOT-OUT-AMT.
          EXIT.
      END-MOCK.
      PERFORM 200-READ-INPUT THRU 200-WRITE.
      *THEN the remaining amount REFTRAN-REMAINING-AMT should be 10000
      EXPECT REFTRAN-REMAINING-AMT TO BE 10000.
